ECCO Modeling Utilities (EMU) is based on computational tools
described by 

  Fukumori, I., Wang, O., & Fenty, I. (2021). Causal Mechanisms of
     Sea-level and Freshwater Content Change in the Beaufort
     Sea. Journal of Physical Oceanography, 51(10),
     3217-3234. https://doi.org/10.1175/jpo-d-21-0069.1

  Fukumori, I., Lee, T., Cheng, B., & Menemenlis, D. (2004). The
     origin, pathway, and destination of Nino-3 water estimated by a
     simulated passive tracer and its adjoint. Journal of Physical
     Oceanography, 34(3),
     582-604. https://doi.org/10.1175/2515.1
